high_descs: Turn left and go to the white drawers in front.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll on the top of the dresser.
Turn left and move through the bathroom to the right side of the toilet.
Pace the empty toilet paper roll on the top of the toilet tank.
Turn around and go to the white shelves on the right.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll on the bottom shelf.
Turn around and go back to the toilet.
Place the second empty toilet paper roll behind the first one on the top of the tank.
anns.task_desc: Put the empty toilet paper roll on the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn left and face the white drawers.
Pick up the tube on the top of the white drawers in the middle of the two bottles of lotion.
Turn and walk over to the toilet on the right.
Put the tube down on the back of the toilet.
Turn and walk to the white counter on the right.
Pick up the tube from the third shelf.
Walk back over to the back of the toilet.
Place the tube on the back of the toilet, to the right of the first tube.
anns.task_desc: To move two tubes to the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around and face the cabinet with bottles on it.
Take the roll.
Walk over to the toilet.
Place the roll on the top of the toilet tank.
Walk over to the cabinet with mirrors over it.
Grab the roll.
Walk over to the toilet.
Put the roll next to the other roll.
anns.task_desc: Put two rolls on the toilet tank.
